{{version030}}
{{Flavour|Spits lava at a targeted creature.}}

'''Spit Lava''' is a monster-only spell. Like [[Bolt of Magma]], it deals 50% irresistible [[fire]] damage. Lava snakes are subject to a [[Breath]] cooldown.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.30]], Spit Lava was 45% irresistible.

[[Category:Monster spells]]
